<plot>In 1815, a young boy named Michael watched the ruthless vampire king Rurik and his brides massacre his family. Twenty three years later Michael is a young man with a vendetta against evil. Once word spreads that Rurik is loose, Michael and his companions set out to track him down and bring justice to his past. The path they travel is corrupt with evil, and Michael's justice turns to revenge, as he is led into a trap giving up the one thing Rurik has always wanted: The family amulet that Michael's father gave him 23 years ago. The amulet is a piece of Michael the Arch Angel's sword, and will give Rurik undying immortal powers and a reign of destruction over man!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?470992</url></doc>
